(320, '2013-09-18', 'Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch Updates Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_11477\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The major changes include:<br><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Updated with other Orange Box client/engine crash fixes<br/></li></ul></br></p>
