(320, '2014-04-25', 'Team Fortress 2, Counter-Strike: Source, Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch Updates Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_13163\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Team Fortress 2, Counter-Strike: Source, Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch have been released. The updates will be applied automatically. The major changes include:<br><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Fixed an issue where compressed community maps would not be decompressed by clients if the file size was too large<br/></li></ul></br></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
